      "rationale": "Bench test conducted at five steady-state operating points matching CFD boundary conditions. Fluid temperature controlled to 37 ± 0.5 °C; viscosity verified by cone-and-plate rheometry. Inlet flow rate uncertainty ±1.5%. All conditions documented in test plan TP-2023-01. Pulsatile inflow waveform characteristic of clinical CPB was not reproduced in bench testing; test conditions reflect steady pump operation only."
