      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Residuals converge to at least 1e-5 for all transport equations; mass imbalance below 0.01%.",
      "rationale": "All simulations converged to continuity residual 1e-6, momentum residuals 5e-6, and hemolysis scalar residual 1e-7. Mass imbalance across pump domain less than 0.005%. Convergence monitored via RH index monitor point; variation below 0.1% over final 500 iterations."
