    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scope. The CFD model predicts RH index within 9.1% of bench measurements across all five COU operating points. The team acknowledges that the Newtonian steady-state model excludes non-Newtonian pulsatile blood rheology present in clinical CPB; an informal internal study was considered sufficient to conclude this exclusion does not materially affect the hemolysis ranking across operating conditions. The credibility package is accepted as adequate to support the regulatory submission claim that the nominal geometry achieves RH < 1 relative to the predicate device.",
